        public static ILineString convertOSMLineToLambert93(OSMWay way,
                                                    Collection<OSMResource> nodes)
        Converts a way into a ILineString using a collection of the nodes, as ways only describe the node id of the vertices. The coordinates are projected in Lambert93 so it doesn't work on non-French data.

        public static IPolygon convertOSMPolygonToLambert93(OSMWay way,
                                                    Collection<OSMResource> nodes)
        Converts a way into a IPolygon using a collection of the nodes, as ways only describe the node id of the vertices. If the way does not represent a polygon, returns null. The coordinates are projected in Lambert93 so it doesn't work on non-French data.
